title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Power Supplies
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the power supply units of a Dell PowerVault ME5 enclosure, including
 health and status.

 State is taken from the power-supply health value reported by the array.
 Conditions are configurable via the "Dell PowerVault ME5 power supply" ruleset.

item:
 The power supply name (for example {"PSU 0, Left"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per power supply.
